 />\n<br />\n就算日本都有大陸做嘅口罩貨，如果佢係高級貨，工廠可靠，都未嘗唔可以平時日常生活用嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我淨係用自己喺日本買返嚟嘅口罩，部份Made in China"},{"pid":"fb514d5ed6f248773daa6f7fefa9ec109b34b3da","tid":1940060,"uid":119167,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/sgshongkong/posts/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fsgshongkong%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1tRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=fb913a64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/sgshongkong/posts/?ref=page_internal</a><br />\n已俾人踢爆佢係不實演繹個檢測<br />\n唔係唔幫MIHK, 但未得唔好吹咩都得囉<br />\n都唔止一間係咁玩啦"},{"pid":"d3a4a26d063e9f337a100eec493f8052d7c0ea79","tid":1940060,"uid":213577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"藍到黑"},{"pid":"270d4ddef18abde12e336685d66ab51d39d1277c","tid":1940060,"uid":277296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb514d5ed6f248773daa6f7fefa9ec109b34b3da","tid":1940060,"uid":119167,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/sgshongkong/posts/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fsgshongkong%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1tRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=fb913a64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/sgshongkong/posts/?ref=page_internal</a><br />\n已俾人踢爆佢係不實演繹個檢測<br />\n唔係唔幫MIHK, 但未得唔好吹咩都得囉<br />\n都唔止一間係咁玩啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"邊係made in hk"},{"pid":"0b4d80db354361a434ac5254d22486bdcb2917b3","tid":1940060,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb514d5ed6f248773daa6f7fefa9ec109b34b3da","tid":1940060,"uid":119167,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.faceboo